        <hl1>QUOTATION OF THE DAY</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''If we don't make this class, and we have no one signing up to take the tests, we will eventually reach a point where we will have no one to make up the shortages, and the department will have to shrink.''</p>
        <p>JOHN DRISCOLL, who heads a union for police officers, on New York's shortage of Police Academy recruits. [A1]</p>
      </block>
